@404 = ~Ah, I suppose I should come clean - confess, even! You see, you have done what so few have before you: you impressed me! I have seen you face many challenges, seen you persevere and come out on top - covered in blood yet righteous in your victory! That's exactly the kind of moxie that will serve you well in my fighting pits.~ // reply 
