@407 = ~You will be a champion, in courageous combat against chilling creatures, to the captivation of cavernous crowds! Your quiescent capacities will be questioned, and we will see if you can transcend my tests and triumph! Up to a point, anyway. It will be glorious! And profitable!~ // reply 312, 413
@408 = ~~
@409 = ~~
@410 = ~~
